Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Gold Star family member Christy Shamblin:"We invited both President Trump and the Biden-Harris administration and we didn't hear back from the White House.""When [President Trump] came to Section 60, it was at our request to spend time with our loved ones. There was no political campaigning done at Section 60 that day.""We support President Trump and he supported us.""I think our media needs to do a better job on focusing on the Afghanistan withdrawal instead of things like this that aren’t really relevant or important."
